Mount Kurusan 狗留孫山 Kurusan-zan | Shimonoseki |  | 10 | [ 2 ]

Oumijima 青海島 Oumijima | Nagato | also a Natural Monument | 5 , 8 | [ 7 ]
Sekichū-kei 石柱渓 Sekichū-kei | Shimonoseki | also a Natural Monument | 5 , 6 | [ 8 ]
Chōmon-kyō 長門峡 Chōmon-kyō | Hagi / Yamaguchi | in Chōmonkyō Prefectural Natural Park | 5 | [ 9 ]
Tawarajima 俵島 Tawarajima | Nagato | also a Natural Monument | 5 , 8 | [ 10 ]
Mōri Family Gardens 毛利氏 庭園 Mōri-shi teien | Hōfu |  | 1 | [ 11 ]
